                                        Why the Panthers will win Super Bowl 50 
                    February 7 2016 1107am EST
                    February 7 2016 1107am EST
                    
                    There are plenty of reasons to be optimistic the Panthers can win the franchise39s first Super Bowl
                
            

                            
                    
                            
    
        
            
                
                    NFL
                
            
            
                
